data.description: Welcome to this gated oceanfront community. This 2-story home features one of the largest lots in the this community and is also only 3 blocks from the beach! The inside is lined up tile flooring throughout the main living area and soaring ceilings. The master bedroom and bath, spacious kitchen /dining area, half bath and laundry room are on the first floor and 2 additional bedrooms, full bath and loft area for office or den on the second floor. HOA fee is $225/month. The HOA provides road maintenance, club house with a pool, guarded gate club house and ocean walk overs. Preferred closing with Title Now LLC. Finance offers may have up to 7 days of inspection. All offers must be accompanied by a POF or a pre-approval letter. ***ACCESS/SHOWING ONLY UPON EXECUTED CONTRACT***
